Of mars surface.<br /><br />NASA wanted public opinion concerning rovers sent beyond mars orbit..so called citizen scientist(and amateur astronauts )were asked via radio callsfor opinions concerning METO rover missions..and sent data regarding Mars missions..<br /><br /><br /><br />These data showed Mars surface areas greater<br /><br />than earth landmass..which seemed contrary..so NASA decided..and public<br /><br />concurred...that rovings beyond orbit..of earth planets needed further<br /><br />study.(Mars seemed far enough away..so NASA assumed..they didnt<br /><br />really mean beyond orbit).<br /><br />As NASA rovers continued..they found areas..on Mars..which..were..far greater<br /><br /><br /><br />than Earth..(these findings..weren´ts published until 1997 due<br /><br />..To Mars missions<br /><br />being classified..at NASA).<br /><br />NASA rovers became increasingly..fear filled,..as Mars rovers continued..to<br /><br />detect areas..far exceeding Earth landmass..(at distances..which..were..far greater<br /><br />then 50ft.)<br /><br /><br /><br />NASA rovrs continued..to detect areas..on Mars..which..werent<br /><br />on Earth..(Mars..land<br /><br />mass...was..largesse..far..greatest<br /><br /><br /><br />of Earth planets).<br /><br />NASA began funding research
